    <item>
      <title>Giới thiệu về Java Cơ bản</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/22DTHE7_KhanhLDD_Blog/blog/java-co-ban/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Dec 2025 10:00:00 +0700</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/22DTHE7_KhanhLDD_Blog/blog/java-co-ban/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;giới-thiệu&#34;&gt;Giới thiệu&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Java là một ngôn ngữ lập trình hướng đối tượng mạnh mẽ, được phát triển bởi Sun Microsystems (nay thuộc Oracle).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;đặc-điểm-chính&#34;&gt;Đặc điểm chính&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hướng đối tượng&lt;/strong&gt;: Java hoàn toàn là ngôn ngữ OOP&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Độc lập nền tảng&lt;/strong&gt;: &amp;ldquo;Write Once, Run Anywhere&amp;rdquo;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bảo mật cao&lt;/strong&gt;: Có nhiều cơ chế bảo mật tích hợp&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Đa luồng&lt;/strong&gt;: Hỗ trợ lập trình đa luồng&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;hello-world-trong-java&#34;&gt;Hello World trong Java&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;HelloWorld&lt;/span&gt; {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;(String&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt; args) {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        System.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, World!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;kết-luận&#34;&gt;Kết luận&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Java là ngôn ngữ lập trình quan trọng cần học cho các lập trình viên.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lập trình Hướng đối tượng trong Java</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/22DTHE7_KhanhLDD_Blog/blog/java-oop/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Dec 2025 10:00:00 +0700</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/22DTHE7_KhanhLDD_Blog/blog/java-oop/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;oop-là-gì&#34;&gt;OOP là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Lập trình hướng đối tượng (OOP - Object-Oriented Programming) là một mô hình lập trình dựa trên khái niệm &amp;ldquo;đối tượng&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;4-tính-chất-cơ-bản-của-oop&#34;&gt;4 Tính chất cơ bản của OOP&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-tính-đóng-gói-encapsulation&#34;&gt;1. Tính đóng gói (Encapsulation)&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Ẩn giấu thông tin và chỉ cho phép truy cập thông qua các phương thức công khai.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Student&lt;/span&gt; {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; String name;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; age;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; String &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;getName&lt;/span&gt;() {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; name;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;setName&lt;/span&gt;(String name) {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; name;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;2-tính-kế-thừa-inheritance&#34;&gt;2. Tính kế thừa (Inheritance)&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Cho phép class con kế thừa các thuộc tính và phương thức từ class cha.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Collection Framework trong Java</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/22DTHE7_KhanhLDD_Blog/blog/java-collections/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Dec 2025 10:00:00 +0700</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/22DTHE7_KhanhLDD_Blog/blog/java-collections/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;collection-framework-là-gì&#34;&gt;Collection Framework là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Collection Framework cung cấp các cấu trúc dữ liệu và thuật toán để lưu trữ và thao tác với nhóm đối tượng.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;các-interface-chính&#34;&gt;Các interface chính&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;list&#34;&gt;List&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Danh sách có thứ tự, cho phép trùng lặp&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Ví dụ: ArrayList, LinkedList&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;List&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;String&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; list &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; ArrayList&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;();&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;list.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;add&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Java&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;list.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;add&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Python&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;list.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;add&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;JavaScript&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;set&#34;&gt;Set&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Tập hợp không cho phép trùng lặp&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Ví dụ: HashSet, TreeSet&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Set&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;Integer&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; set &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; HashSet&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;();&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;set.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;add&lt;/span&gt;(1);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;set.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;add&lt;/span&gt;(2);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;set.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;add&lt;/span&gt;(1); &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// Không thêm được vì trùng&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;map&#34;&gt;Map&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Lưu trữ cặp key-value&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Ví dụ: HashMap, TreeMap&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Map&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;String, Integer&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; map &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; HashMap&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;();&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;map.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;put&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Java&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, 1);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;map.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;put&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Python&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, 2);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;kết-luận&#34;&gt;Kết luận&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Collection Framework là công cụ quan trọng trong Java để quản lý dữ liệu hiệu quả.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Exception Handling trong Java</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/22DTHE7_KhanhLDD_Blog/blog/java-exception/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Dec 2025 10:00:00 +0700</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/22DTHE7_KhanhLDD_Blog/blog/java-exception/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;exception-là-gì&#34;&gt;Exception là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Exception là một sự kiện xảy ra trong quá trình thực thi chương trình, làm gián đoạn luồng thực thi bình thường.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;cách-xử-lý-exception&#34;&gt;Cách xử lý Exception&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;try-catch&#34;&gt;Try-Catch&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; result &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; 10 &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; 0;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (ArithmeticException e) {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    System.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Không thể chia cho 0!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;finally&lt;/span&gt; {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    System.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Luôn được thực thi&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;các-loại-exception&#34;&gt;Các loại Exception&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;checked-exception&#34;&gt;Checked Exception&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Phải được xử lý tại compile time&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Ví dụ: IOException, SQLException&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;unchecked-exception&#34;&gt;Unchecked Exception&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Không bắt buộc xử lý&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Ví dụ: NullPointerException, ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;throw-và-throws&#34;&gt;Throw và Throws&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;validateAge&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; age) &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; InvalidAgeException {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (age &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; 18) {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; InvalidAgeException(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Tuổi phải &amp;gt;= 18&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;kết-luận&#34;&gt;Kết luận&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Xử lý exception đúng cách giúp chương trình ổn định và dễ debug hơn.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Stream API trong Java 8</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/22DTHE7_KhanhLDD_Blog/blog/java-stream-api/</link>
